line_1: And now to artful steps the floor rebounds,
line_2: The noice like thunder at a distance sounds,

line_1: While Melody from yon steep wood rebounds
line_2: Here the soft turf invites; here magic sounds

line_1: Crash the shock'd masts, the staggering wreck rebounds;
line_2: — Dash'd in dread conflict on the rocky grounds,
